title: Total Overdose: A Gunslinger's Tale in Mexico (PS2) (NTSC) (Fabi
description:
Total Overdose: A Gunslinger's Tale in Mexico (PS2)

Region: NTSC

Year: 2005

Developed by the Danish production house Deadline, Overdose puts players in the role of an undercover DEA agent charged with the mission of infiltrating a Mexican drug cartel and taking it apart from the inside out. Built using a new proprietary engine that was created in-house by Deadline, the game's other details remain unannounced.
